    </div>
    <div class="educational-text">
        <p><strong>Dietary Considerations:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide consistent, high-quality forage</li>
            <li>Minimize sudden dietary changes</li>
            <li>Avoid excessive grain feeding</li>
            <li>Consider prebiotic supplementation</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Management Practices:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Reduce stress through consistent routines</li>
            <li>Limit unnecessary antibiotic use</li>
            <li>Provide adequate exercise and turnout</li>
            <li>Monitor for signs of digestive upset</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
{% endmacro %}

